cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY

This paper is about natural language processing and corpus creation, which falls under the category of cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also mentions the use of deep learning, which is a popular technique in the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The corpus is also relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) as it can be used to improve search results for informal Chinese language. Finally, the paper mentions the potential use of the corpus for sentiment analysis (cs.CY), which is a sub-category of computational social science.
